# The Consul de# The Consul de# The Consul de# Th KB (# The Consul de# The Consul de# The Consul de# Th KB (# The Consul de# The Consullicat# The Consul it# The Consnsul'# The Consul de# The Consul de# The Consul de# Th KB (# The Consul de# The Consultor# The Consul de# The Consul de# The Consul de# Th KB (# The Consul de# The Consul de# mandat# The Consul de# The Consul de# The Consul de# Th KB (# The Consul de# The Consul de#dator# The Consul de# The Consul de# The Consul de# Th KB alue# The Consul de# The Consul de# The Consul de# Th KB (# The Consul de#see # The Consul de# The Consul de# The Consul de# Th KB (# The Consul de# The Consul de536 # The Consul de# The Consul de# The Consul de# Th2      # 512 B   — keeps key paths short and readable

# --------------------------------------------# --------------------------------------------# -- b# ---hin the size limit
# length() returns the number of UTF-8 code points; for # length() returns the number of U t# lenge # length() returns the number ofe-case.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
value_within_limit = rule {
  length(value) <= max_value_bytes
}

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Rule: key path must be within the size limit
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
key_within_limit = rule {
  length(key) <= max_key_bytes
}

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Main rule: both key and value must be within their respective size limits.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
main = rule {
  value_within_limit and key_within_limit
}
